               <msContents>
                  <summary>ʾArbāʿtu wangel: I) Gospel of Matthew (incomplete, folios misplaced)
                     - Bǝsrāta Mātewos "Gospel of Matthew" (fols. 1ra-2vb, 7ra-vb, 9ra-10vb,
                     11ra-vb, 12ra-vb, 38ra-39vb, 40ra-47vb, 48ra-53vb, 54ra-61vb, 71ra-77vb,
                     80ra-vb, 100ra-vb, 147ra-vb, 149ra-vb, 150ra-vb) 
 II) Gospel of Mark
                     (incomplete, folios misplaced)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of
                     Mark: 37 titles (fol. 81ra-rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos "Gospel of Mark" (fols.
                     22ra-28va, 63ra-70vb, 83ra-87vb, 104ra-105vb, 131ra-138vb)
 III) Gospel of
                     Luke (incomplete, folios misplaced)
 - List of the “tituli” of the Gospel
                     of Luke, incomplete (fol. 28va-vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās "Gospel of Luke" (fols.
                     14ra-21vb, 37ra-37vb, 62ra-vb, 94ra-95vb, 96ra-99vb, 101ra-vb, 102ra-103vb,
                     106ra-107vb, 108ra, 126rb, 148ra-vb)
 IV) Gospel of John (incomplete,
                     folios misplaced)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 18 titles
                     (fol. 126va)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs "Gospel of John" (fols. 3ra-6vb, 8ra-vb,
                     13ra-vb, 29ra-36vb, 78ra-79vb, 88ra-94vb, 127ra-130vb, 139ra-146vb,
                     151ra-154rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
